%N A394628 Indices of records in A133422, the number of iterations to reach 1 under the 7x+1 map A133421.
%C A394628 The 7x+1 map A133421 yields x/p if p = smallest prime factor < 7 of x, or 7x+1 if there's no such p.
%F A394628 a(n+1) <= 2*a(n) with equality for n = 1, 2, 9, 15, 25, 28, 33, 35, 39, 40...
%e A394628 The records are as follows:
%e A394628    n | a(n) = starting value m | record value A133422(m) > A133422(k) for all k < m
%e A394628  ----+-------------------------+---------------------------------------------------
%e A394628    1 |             1           |   0
%e A394628    2 |             2           |   1
%e A394628    3 |             4           |   2
%e A394628    4 |             7           |   4
%e A394628    5 |            11           |  12
%e A394628    6 |            19           |  21
%e A394628    7 |            31           |  47
%e A394628    8 |            49           |  50
%e A394628    9 |            53           |  51
%e A394628   10 |           106           |  52
%e A394628   11 |           121           |  56
%e A394628   12 |           163           |  58
%e A394628   13 |           283           |  61
%e A394628   14 |           343           |  85
%e A394628   15 |           403           |  92
%e A394628   16 |           806           |  93
%e A394628   17 |          1471           | 105
%e A394628   18 |          1681           | 109
%e A394628   19 |          1919           | 115
%e A394628   20 |          3133           | 122
%e A394628   21 |          4243           | 127
%e A394628  ... |           ...           | ...
%o A394628 (PARI) my(r=-1); for(n=1,oo, A133422(n)>r && print1(n", ")+r=A133422(n))
%o A394628 (Python)
%o A394628 def A394628(n):
%o A394628     while len(T := A394628.T) < n:
%o A394628         N = T[-1]+1; R = A133422(N-1)
%o A394628         while A133422(N) <= R: N += 1
%o A394628         T.append(N)
%o A394628     return T[n-1]
%o A394628 A394628.T = [1]
%Y A394628 Cf. A394627 (same for P=5), A133421 (the 7x+1 map), A133422 (number of iterations to reach 1).
%K A394628 nonn,new
%O A394628 1,2
